---
layout: _layouts/base.njk
title: Home
---
<style>
  /* ── Hero ─────────────────────────────────────────────── */
  .hero {
    padding-bottom: 4rem;
    margin-bottom: 4rem;
    max-width: 680px;
  }

  .hero-eyebrow {
    display: block;
    font-size: 0.68rem;
    font-weight: 300;
    letter-spacing: 0.22em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--accent);
    margin-bottom: 1.75rem;
  }

  .hero-heading {
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 6vw, 4.5rem);
    font-weight: 300;
    line-height: 1.1;
    color: var(--text-1);
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .hero-heading em {
    font-style: italic;
    font-weight: 300;
    color: var(--accent);
  }

  .hero-sub {
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    font-weight: 400;
    color: var(--text-2);
    line-height: 1.8;
    max-width: 480px;
    letter-spacing: 0.01em;
  }

  /* ── Journal section ─────────────────────────────────── */
  .section-header {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
  }

  .section-label {
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    font-weight: 400;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--text-2);
    white-space: nowrap;
  }

  .section-rule {
    flex: 1;
    height: 1px;
    background: var(--border);
  }

  /* ── Article cards ───────────────────────────────────── */
  .articles-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(320px, 1fr));
    gap: 1.5rem;
  }

  .article-card {
    background: var(--bg-card);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    padding: 2rem;
    text-decoration: none;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    position: relative;
    transition: border-color 0.3s, box-shadow 0.3s;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  /* Left accent bar — rises on hover */
  .article-card::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    left: 0; top: 0; bottom: 0;
    width: 2px;
    background: var(--accent);
    transform: scaleY(0);
    transform-origin: bottom;
    transition: transform 0.4s ease;
  }

  .article-card:hover {
    border-color: rgba(184, 147, 90, 0.38);
    box-shadow: 0 4px 28px rgba(184, 147, 90, 0.07), 0 1px 6px rgba(28, 24, 20, 0.04);
  }

  .article-card:hover::before { transform: scaleY(1); }

  .card-tags {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .card-tag {
    font-size: 0.65rem;
    font-weight: 400;
    letter-spacing: 0.15em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--accent-rose);
    border: 1px solid var(--border-rose);
    padding: 0.2rem 0.6rem;
    border-radius: 1px;
  }

  .card-title {
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    font-weight: 400;
    color: var(--text-1);
    line-height: 1.2;
    margin-bottom: 0.85rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.01em;
  }

  .card-summary {
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    font-weight: 400;
    color: var(--text-2);
    line-height: 1.75;
    flex: 1;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.01em;
  }

  .card-footer {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    gap: 1rem;
    padding-top: 1.25rem;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
  }

  .card-date {
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    font-weight: 300;
    letter-spacing: 0.14em;
    color: var(--text-3);
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  .card-read {
    font-size: 0.68rem;
    font-weight: 400;
    letter-spacing: 0.14em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--accent);
    transition: letter-spacing 0.35s ease;
  }

  .article-card:hover .card-read { letter-spacing: 0.22em; }

  .empty-state {
    padding: 3rem 0;
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    font-style: italic;
    font-weight: 300;
    color: var(--text-3);
  }

  /* ── Services ───────────────────────────────────────────── */
  .services-section {
    margin-bottom: 5rem;
  }

  .service-block {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 5rem;
    align-items: center;
    padding: 4.5rem 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
  }

  .service-block:first-of-type { padding-top: 0; }
  .service-block:last-of-type { border-bottom: none; }

  .service-block--alt .service-image { order: 2; }
  .service-block--alt .service-content { order: 1; }

  /* Placeholder — replace figure contents with <img> when photos are ready */
  .service-image {
    aspect-ratio: 4 / 3;
    background:
      linear-gradient(rgba(184, 147, 90, 0.055) 1px, transparent 1px),
      linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(184, 147, 90, 0.055) 1px, transparent 1px),
      linear-gradient(135deg, #f4eee5 0%, #ece3d6 100%);
    background-size: 28px 28px, 28px 28px, 100% 100%;
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .service-image img {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
    display: block;
  }

  .placeholder-icon { width: 40px; height: 40px; }

  .service-number {
    display: block;
    font-size: 0.62rem;
    font-weight: 300;
    letter-spacing: 0.25em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--accent);
    margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
  }

  .service-title {
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-size: clamp(1.75rem, 3vw, 2.25rem);
    font-weight: 300;
    color: var(--text-1);
    line-height: 1.15;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.01em;
  }

  .service-subtitle {
    display: block;
    font-size: 0.68rem;
    font-weight: 300;
    letter-spacing: 0.2em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--accent-rose);
    margin-bottom: 1.75rem;
  }

  .service-desc {
    font-size: 1rem;
    font-weight: 400;
    color: var(--text-2);
    line-height: 1.85;
    letter-spacing: 0.01em;
    margin-bottom: 1.75rem;
  }

  .service-includes {
    list-style: none;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .service-includes li {
    font-size: 0.92rem;
    font-weight: 400;
    color: var(--text-2);
    letter-spacing: 0.01em;
    padding: 0.5rem 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.85rem;
  }

  .service-includes li::before {
    content: '';
    width: 18px;
    height: 1px;
    background: var(--accent);
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .service-cta {
    display: inline-block;
    font-size: 0.68rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.2em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--text-1);
    text-decoration: none;
    padding-bottom: 0.35rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--accent);
    transition: color 0.25s, letter-spacing 0.35s ease;
  }

  .service-cta:hover {
    color: var(--accent);
    letter-spacing: 0.28em;
  }

  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .service-block {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 2.5rem;
      padding: 3rem 0;
    }
    .service-block--alt .service-image { order: 0; }
    .service-block--alt .service-content { order: 1; }
  }

  /* ── About ───────────────────────────────────────────── */
  .about-section {
    margin-bottom: 5rem;
  }

  .about-content {
    max-width: 680px;
  }

  .about-text {
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    font-weight: 400;
    color: var(--text-2);
    line-height: 1.85;
    letter-spacing: 0.01em;
  }

  .about-text p { margin-bottom: 1.4rem; }

  @media (max-width: 640px) {
    .articles-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .hero { padding-bottom: 2.5rem; margin-bottom: 2.5rem; }
  }
</style>

<section class="hero">
  <span class="hero-eyebrow" data-i18n="tagline">Interior Design &amp; Architecture</span>
  <h1 class="hero-heading">
    <span data-i18n="heroLine1">Spaces that</span><br>
    <em data-i18n="heroEm">speak to the soul.</em>
  </h1>
  <p class="hero-sub" data-i18n="heroSub">{{ site.description }}</p>
</section>

<section class="services-section">
  <div class="section-header">
    <span class="section-label" data-i18n="services">Services</span>
    <div class="section-rule"></div>
  </div>

  <div class="service-block">
    <figure class="service-image" aria-label="Full project interior design">
      <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1586023492125-27b2c045efd7?w=800&h=600&fit=crop&crop=center&auto=format" alt="Interior design project with natural light and elegant finishes">
    </figure>
    <div class="service-content">
      <span class="service-number">01</span>
      <h2 class="service-title" data-i18n="s1title">Full Project</h2>
      <span class="service-subtitle" data-i18n="s1sub">Design &middot; Construction &middot; Management</span>
      <p class="service-desc" data-i18n="s1desc">From the first sketch to the final finish, we guide every phase of your project. Our comprehensive service covers spatial planning, material selection, contractor coordination, and on-site management &mdash; ensuring your vision is realised with precision and care, on time and to budget.</p>
      <ul class="service-includes">
        <li data-i18n="s1i1">Concept design &amp; spatial planning</li>
        <li data-i18n="s1i2">Material, finish &amp; furniture specification</li>
        <li data-i18n="s1i3">Contractor sourcing &amp; coordination</li>
        <li data-i18n="s1i4">Construction oversight &amp; site visits</li>
        <li data-i18n="s1i5">Final delivery &amp; styling</li>
      </ul>
      <a href="mailto:hello@helena.studio" class="service-cta" data-i18n="s1cta">Start a project</a>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="service-block service-block--alt">
    <figure class="service-image" aria-label="Turnkey design for construction">
      <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1616486338812-3dadae4b4ace?w=800&h=600&fit=crop&crop=center&auto=format" alt="Modern architectural interior with clean lines and premium materials">
    </figure>
    <div class="service-content">
      <span class="service-number">02</span>
      <h2 class="service-title" data-i18n="s2title">Turnkey Design</h2>
      <span class="service-subtitle" data-i18n="s2sub">For Constructors &amp; Developers</span>
      <p class="service-desc" data-i18n="s2desc">We partner with construction companies and developers to deliver complete interior design packages ready for immediate execution. Our documentation, specifications, and material schedules are built for efficiency &mdash; allowing your teams to build with confidence from day one.</p>
      <ul class="service-includes">
        <li data-i18n="s2i1">Full design documentation &amp; technical drawings</li>
        <li data-i18n="s2i2">Material &amp; product schedules</li>
        <li data-i18n="s2i3">Supplier coordination</li>
        <li data-i18n="s2i4">Fit-out ready handover package</li>
      </ul>
      <a href="mailto:hello@helena.studio" class="service-cta" data-i18n="s2cta">Work with us</a>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="service-block">
    <figure class="service-image" aria-label="Interior design consulting">
      <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1512917774080-9991f1c4c750?w=800&h=600&fit=crop&crop=center&auto=format" alt="Interior design consultation with architectural drawings and materials">
    </figure>
    <div class="service-content">
      <span class="service-number">03</span>
      <h2 class="service-title" data-i18n="s3title">Consulting</h2>
      <span class="service-subtitle" data-i18n="s3sub">Expert Guidance, On Demand</span>
      <p class="service-desc" data-i18n="s3desc">Not every project requires a full design engagement. Our consulting service provides targeted expertise &mdash; space planning, material advice, project review, or a second opinion &mdash; delivered with the depth of a full studio relationship and the flexibility to meet you where you are.</p>
      <ul class="service-includes">
        <li data-i18n="s3i1">Space planning &amp; layout review</li>
        <li data-i18n="s3i2">Material &amp; palette advice</li>
        <li data-i18n="s3i3">Project audit &amp; troubleshooting</li>
        <li data-i18n="s3i4">Single session or ongoing retainer</li>
      </ul>
      <a href="mailto:hello@helena.studio" class="service-cta" data-i18n="s3cta">Book a session</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="about-section">
  <div class="section-header">
    <span class="section-label" data-i18n="about">About</span>
    <div class="section-rule"></div>
  </div>

  <div class="about-content">
    <div class="about-text">
      <p data-i18n="aboutP1">Helena is an interior design and architecture studio founded on the belief that spaces should reflect the people who inhabit them. With over a decade of experience across residential, commercial, and hospitality projects, we bring a thoughtful, detail-oriented approach to every commission.</p>
      <p data-i18n="aboutP2">Our work balances timeless elegance with contemporary sensibility — drawing on classical principles while embracing modern materials and techniques. We collaborate closely with clients, craftsmen, and contractors to ensure that every project is realised with precision and care.</p>
      <p data-i18n="aboutP3">Based in Geneva, we work across Switzerland and internationally, bringing the same level of attention and craftsmanship to every scale of project, from intimate residential renovations to large-scale commercial developments.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="articles-section">
  <div class="section-header">
    <span class="section-label" data-i18n="portfolio">Portfolio</span>
    <div class="section-rule"></div>
  </div>

  {% if collections.article.length %}
  <div class="articles-grid">
    {% for article in collections.article %}
    <a href="{{ article.url | url }}" class="article-card" data-article-key="{{ article.page.url }}">
      {% if article.data.tags %}
      <div class="card-tags">
        {% for tag in article.data.tags %}
          <span class="card-tag">{{ tag }}</span>
        {% endfor %}
      </div>
      {% endif %}

      <div class="card-title" data-card-field="title" data-orig="{{ article.data.title | escape }}">{{ article.data.title }}</div>

      {% if article.data.summary %}
      <div class="card-summary" data-card-field="summary" data-orig="{{ article.data.summary | escape }}">{{ article.data.summary }}</div>
      {% endif %}

      <div class="card-footer">
        <span class="card-date">{{ article.date | date("MMM dd, yyyy") }}</span>
        <span class="card-read" data-i18n="read">Read</span>
      </div>
    </a>
    {% endfor %}
  </div>
  {% else %}
  <p class="empty-state">No articles yet — check back soon.</p>
  {% endif %}
</section>
<script>
window._articleTrans={
  {% for article in collections.article %}{% if article.data.translations %}{{ article.page.url | dump | safe }}:{{ article.data.translations | dump | safe }},{% endif %}{% endfor %}
};
</script>
